sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant ProdApp as PROD mobile app
  participant ProdBackend as PROD backend
  participant Slash as Handoff action
  participant Queue as DEV handoff queue
  participant Audit as Handoff audit log
  participant DevWorker as DEV backlog worker

  User->>ProdApp: Select conversation context
  User->>ProdApp: Invoke DEV handoff action
  ProdApp->>ProdBackend: Request temporary handoff mode
  ProdBackend->>Slash: Load narrow handoff contract
  Slash->>Slash: Validate enqueue-only capabilities
  Slash->>Queue: Create immutable handoff with idempotency key
  Queue->>Audit: Persist source session and redacted evidence
  Queue-->>Slash: queued item id
  Slash-->>ProdBackend: Confirmation only
  ProdBackend-->>ProdApp: Handoff queued
  ProdApp-->>User: Show queued item id
  Queue-->>DevWorker: Item available for DEV claim

  Note over Slash,Queue: No file edits, shell commands, restarts, git operations, or DEV agent launches are available.

